#include <iostream>
#include <algorithm>
using namespace std;
 
int main()
{
	long t,n;
	cin>>t;
	while(t--)
	{
		cin>>n;
		long * ptr = (long *)calloc(n,sizeof(long));
		for(long i = 0; i < n; i++) cin >> ptr[i];
		sort(ptr,ptr+n);
		for(long i = 0; i < n; i++) cout<< ptr[i] << " ";
		cout << endl;
	}
	return 0;
}
